Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FIELD OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing older has changed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of a Darkling is uneventful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We live much longer than humans,\Nso many of us are lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some lives can last centuries\Nyet still be empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious. Not many\Ncan feel what I feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I feel truly fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword was well forged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an incredible power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword has a soul.\NIt chooses when and where it fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. A weapon this destructive\Nshouldn't be used just anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you seal yourself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only borrow your strength to fight\Ntruly powerful enemies or save everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to have you with me, my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have gone\Nto help the others fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still one more\Nsource of evil energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy leader wasn't in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense something horrible\Nis about to erupt forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all...\NPopp and the others are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have lost your trump card,\Nbut this is unlike you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wide open, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Air Strike!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He didn't even try to dodge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's his Dark Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a... disgraceful failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Ban's\NSovereign Rock Castle in ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because I failed to realize\Nthe power of Dai's new sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get\Nfor underestimating us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to finish you with my spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, Popp! Don't attack recklessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yow, yow, yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He reflected my spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was like he amplified it\Nand fired it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its impact was closer to\Nthat of a Begiragon spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dark Puppetry Aura Decimation Field\Nand Byut Deathstringer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they just a fraction\Nof his true power?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I must shed my Shadow Raiment\Nand erase Dai and all of you right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when you shall realize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,being crushed by Sovereign Rock Castle\Nor being torn apart by my Dark Aura
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,would have been a far better way to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that giant castle,\Nthe pressure coming from Mystban is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always assumed the source\Nof Mystban's power was his Dark Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that Dark Aura\Nwasn't his greatest weapon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it just have been a veil\Nhiding his true form?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now witness my true power...\NThe power of Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...And stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough right there, Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kilban, the Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad boy! Bad boy!\NKing Ban's gonna be mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true form,\Nno matter the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be revealed\Nwith King Ban's permission, can it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Disobey that and, friend or not,\NI'll be forced to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize! Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign Rock Castle is only\None of King Ban's many toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With a sincere apology, he's sure\Nto forgive his precious little Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Better that than\Nadding to your shame here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I will never fail again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's back to silent mode, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everybody, with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll be excusing ourselves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's sword was quite impressive,\Ndestroying Sovereign Rock Castle and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him congratulations on completing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he doesn't have to worry\Nabout his friends being useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, especially you. You couldn't\Ndo a thing to Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that...\NAfter all you did to this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can insult us\Nand get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You won't get away!\NThis time, I'm finding your stronghold!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? I sensed a huge power here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp flew off alone\Nchasing after the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one here\Nwho can catch up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! You have to bring Popp back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost his cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They went northwest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you know that\Nthe power of Dai's crest is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd expect Dai to have flown back here\Nafter destroying Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But he came on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have spent a lot of energy\Ndestroying Sovereign Rock Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was subunconsciously\Nconserving his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a choice.\NPopp was heading to certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban is the one tasked\Nwith killing us Legion Commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No one in the Dark Army\Nhas ever seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If he ever appeared before anyone,\Nit would mean their death was certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's that dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you have to bring Popp back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't fight... head-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,north of Orzam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so focused on flying.\NCould this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Field of Death?!\NIs this the stronghold of the Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:11.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TOMAKUGUTSOSHO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake.\NThis is the infamous Field of Death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some call it the world's edge\Nor the last unexplored land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a dark island devoid of any life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one has ever approached it\Nand returned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it. It's the perfect place\Nfor the Dark Army to use as a base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet Ban, the Dark King, is here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may have gotten in over my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to learn to control myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A flute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kilban!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Both of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think you could\Nkeep up with us if we were serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We flew slow enough so you could\Nand you fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy! Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?! Then why reveal\Nwhere your stronghold is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You Disciples of Aban\Nhave grown rather strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I should get around\Nto doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your job?! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something felt very wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you've guessed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I'm dressed, my title of Reaper,\Nand everything I've said and done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As-sas-si-na-tion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the...?! His scythe\Nwasn't even close to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that, dumb reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn! Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! What's going on here?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I dreaming?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's something far more grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An illusion! He's somehow\Nmaking me see illusions!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How?! How is he doing it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't see him cast a spell\Nand he didn't use any items!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This high-pitched, whistling noise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like... a flute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you'd realized it\Na few seconds earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the...?! I can't see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move either!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?! Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My Reaper Flute isn't just\Nfor playing sweet melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I use it like this for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I swing my scythe,\Nair flows through the flute,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which emits a high-frequency tone\Nthat can barely be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon entering the ears,\Nthis sound disrupts my opponents' vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it robs them\Nof all of their senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called the Reaper Flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect weapon\Nfor assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You pathetic dummy! Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mock him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaklings like him who improve a little\Nbecome the heart and soul of their team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the first of the Hero's party\Nyou'd want to get rid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we lured him here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kill him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Piroro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed us, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! We almost got to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Myst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you need to be careful of\NDai, the Hero, when he has that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, be careful! His Reaper Flute...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! The Reaper Flute\Nisn't working?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The Reaper Flute is cracked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it when he blocked me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good going, Dai! He uses that flute\Nto create illusions to kill his enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By cracking it, you prevented him\Nfrom controlling the sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't pursue them any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find an opening and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is if they'll let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like both sides\Nare out of decisive moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They still have their trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We both want to finish this,\Nand we both want to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is frustrating.\NNeither side can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sword won't come out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free of the illusions now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stalemate.\NLet's attack and break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You were alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have kept you waiting, Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fully powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered up?! Nothing's changed about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you will fight me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One on one. Fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You're one to talk about fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cast aside my useless pride\Nand even my Darkling body for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have but one wish left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat you,\Nthe legacy of my eternal rival, Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sword! It opened its seal by itself?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My sword realizes that Hadorra\Nis far more powerful than ever before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't use your crest at full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to conserve your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He's not the Hadorra we knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to fight\Nwith my full strength or we'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,An astute observation!\NYou truly are my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect nothing less\Nfrom a Disciple of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:48.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:16.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra appeared before\NDai and Popp with new power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai struggles against his awesome power,\Neven with his full Dragonic Aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra's power and his resolve\Nare beyond anything ever before,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}forcing Dai to wield his sword once more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Clash of Powerful Swords"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
